            <h2 itemprop="headline">Hi, I'm Joonie Mae</h2>
            <p itemprop="description">
                I've been an avid fan and consumer of ASMR for the last several years. And because of that,
				I thought why not make more of the sounds I'd like to hear? So I set up an experiment
				where I challenged myself to consistently create and publish ASMR videos for the next six
				months. Ultimately, I created my channel for myself; for the times where I like to read
				and have an ASMR video playing in the background. 
				I hope you all can take something away from my creations - whether it calmed you down, 
				put you to sleep, or made you reflective. Thank you for supporting me!
            </p>
